attachments.title: Senior Russian diplomat shot dead in flat in Moscow hours before ambassador's assassination
attachments.text: A high-ranking Russian diplomat has reportedly been found dead from a gunshot wound at his Moscow home.  Local media reported a senior civil servant in the Foreign Ministry was found dead at his home in the Balaklavsky Prospekt apartment block with a bullet wound in the head. The victim has since been named as Petr Polshikov, 56 – who was the chief adviser to the Latin American department at the ministry.
attachments.fallback: The Independent: Senior Russian diplomat shot dead in flat in Moscow hours before ambassador's assassination
